  "keyFeatures": [
    "Five CPU scheduling algorithms (FIFO, SJF, Round Robin, Priority, MLFQ)",
    "Real-time visual simulation with Gantt charts and process queues",
    "Interactive process configuration with arrival times, CPU bursts, and priorities",
    "Performance metrics calculation (waiting time, turnaround time)",
    "Responsive design with Tailwind CSS",
    "Zero backend dependencies - runs entirely in browser"
